{"tid":1751114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"假設有70％選民投票率","createTime":"2019-11-24T16:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T17:18:36.000Z","uid":290815,"like":107,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6911ffffc89fe1cff4ec5b341ac1d3602b424f","tid":1751114,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:00:25.000Z","msg":"即係10個選民入面有7個去咗投票，咁淨低嗰3個去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？暈咗？<br />\n<br />\n個人認為一個「公投」既投票率可以好高亦可以好低，但去到7成依個尷尬數字，即係好似你同你阿媽帶住爺爺嫲嫲好迫不及待去投票，<span style=\"color: red;\">然後你阿爸同阿哥講「唔喇都唔關我哋事」</span>咁樣。講緊唔係一個家庭，而係幾十萬個家庭。<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就係特別有好多個家族完全遠離民生同政治，而且係打咗幾個月街頭抗爭既環境下，依然堅守家族理念，「<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋不干預世事！完全中立！</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？咁我想請問一句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢哋申請選民嚟做乜？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔嗲唔吊咁，硬係覺得有啲唔爽。<br />\n<br />\nanyway，祝香港前程錦繡，大比數拋離保皇黨！！<br />\n<br />\n要show畀國際睇香港問題既巖峻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccef686612748d63e8f129f7ead1946227504b33","tid":1751114,"uid":36238,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"嗰啲咪就係返大灣區都無所謂嘅人"},{"pid":"50b044160abe43c83d824e7f971f5a650892eacd","tid":1751114,"uid":156258,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:03:01.000Z","msg":"外遊 外地公幹 住係外國"},{"pid":"55e79a8695ca323bc70212b1002e58e02c267233","tid":1751114,"uid":214036,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7a1b3d01f3b47aef2448e6f5d49682859f4ef7b","tid":1751114,"uid":290815,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:04:02.000Z","msg":"佢哋登記做選民嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as